Description: modern CDE-like desktop environment
 NsCDE is a retro but powerful desktop environment inspired by the
 Common Desktop Environment. It provides a CDE-like workflow, front panel,
 window management configuration, icons, color management, and desktop
 integration on top of FVWM.

Package: nscde-data
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ksh93u+m,
 python3:any,
 python3-psutil,
 python3-pyqt5,
 python3-xdg,
 python3-yaml
Description: data files for NsCDE
 This package contains architecture-independent data files used by NsCDE,
 including FVWM configuration, palettes, backdrops, templates, integration
 files, localization files, and supporting scripts.

Package: nscde-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: icon theme for NsCDE
 This package contains the NsCDE icon theme used by the NsCDE desktop
 environment and its XDG desktop integration.

Package: nscde-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: documentation for NsCDE
 This package contains user documentation, examples, release notes, and
 HTML/PDF documentation for the NsCDE desktop environment.
